OL,3,CWelsh peer becomes youngest member of
OL,4,CHouse of Lords
OL,6,FA Plaid Cymru nominee has been
OL,7,Fappointed the youngest member of the
OL,8,FHouse of Lords.
OL,10,FCarmen Smith, aged just 27, was the
OL,11,Fparty's only nomination for the UK
OL,12,FParliament's second chamber.
OL,14,FMs Smith's new role has been
OL,15,Fofficially approved by the King,
OL,16,Fmeaning she will join Plaid Cymru's
OL,17,Fthree MPs and one Lord - Lord Wigley -
OL,18,Fin Westminster.
