OL,6,FShe will become the youngest Lord by
OL,7,Fthree years, with the title previously
OL,8,Fheld by Boris Johnson's former advisor
OL,9,FCharlotte Owen.
OL,11,FA former Plaid Cymru advisor, Ms Smith
OL,12,Fsaid: "I am looking forward to joining
OL,13,Fthe Plaid Cymru team in Westminster
OL,14,Fand getting to work on behalf of the
OL,15,Fpeople of Wales. That task is an
OL,16,Furgent one, and I am eager to play my
OL,17,Fpart.
