OL,3,CWelsh peer becomes youngest member of
OL,4,CHouse of Lords
OL,6,F"Alongside our MPs, I will be fighting
OL,7,Ffor a fair deal for Wales and holding
OL,8,Fthis and future UK governments to
OL,9,Faccount. I will be unashamed in
OL,10,Fadvocating for a fairer, more
OL,11,Fsustainable, and ultimately
OL,12,Findependent future for Cymru."
OL,14,FShe added: "As a young woman, I will
OL,15,Fwork to inspire the next generation of
OL,16,Fwomen to take an active role in our
OL,17,Fcommunities and our nation."
OL,19,FAs a party, Plaid Cymru is opposed to
OL,20,Fthe House of Lords.
