OL,6,FHowever, in a statement the party
OL,7,Fsaid: "Wherever Wales is debated,
OL,8,FWales must be represented."
OL,10,FThe party appointed its only other
OL,11,Fmember of the House of Lords in 2011.
OL,13,FThe former chief of staff for the
OL,14,FWelsh Senedd Plaid Cymru group is not
OL,15,Fthe only person to have been
OL,16,Fnominated, with eight put new peers
OL,17,Fapproved from the UK Conservatives and
OL,18,Ffour from UK Labour.
