OL,6,F"We need as many Plaid Cymru voices as
OL,7,Fpossible in Westminster to demand
OL,8,Ffairness and ambition for Wales - I
OL,9,Fknow Carmen will deliver at every
OL,10,Fopportunity.
OL,12,F"We will continue to oppose the
OL,13,Funelected second chamber resolutely as
OL,14,Fa matter of principle, but, while it
OL,15,Fexists, Plaid Cymru believes in
OL,16,Fensuring that wherever Wales is
OL,17,Fdebated, that Wales is represented.
